IMPACTED BY UNFAVORABLE ECONOMIC CONDITIONS IN PARTS OF THE REGION REFLECTED BY SECOND HALF 2013 NET SALES FALLING 4% COMPARED TO THE SECOND HALF OF 2012, WHICH FOLLOWED AN 11% INCREASE IN NET SALES DURING THE FIRST HALF OF 2013.

