IN THE THIRD QUARTER OF 2013, THE COMPANY RAISED ITS CASH DIVIDEND BY 15% TO $3.05 PER COMMON SHARE. THE COMPANY EXPECTS TO CONTINUE TO PAY QUARTERLY DIVIDENDS OF $3.05 PER COMMON SHARE EACH QUARTER,

SUBJECT TO DECLARATION BY THE BOARD OF DIRECTORS.

